Package hamlet.alexander.SpeakEasy

Class SessionView

  • java.lang.Object
    • hamlet.alexander.SpeakEasy.SessionView
  • @Component
public class SessionView
extends java.lang.Object
    MODEL VIEW CONTROLLER DESIGN PATTER: View The SessionView is the object that handles setting up each page, and displaying each page for viewing. To make the website view work accordingly, the SessionView uses mustache templates to display the different pages. Those can be found under ..../src/main/resources/templates.
